The evidence with the title 'HIV and hepatitis c | AVERT ' says Jul 27, 2017  ...  ... Malawi · South Africa · eswatini · Tanzania · Uganda · Zambia · Zimbabwe  ... . 2.3 million people have HIV and hepatitis c co-infection – 6.2% of people  ... Each year, an estimated 700,000 people die from complications of hepatitis C.2  ... More rapid hepatitis disease progression than HIV-negative people. 
